  "url": "https://www.nps.gov/grca/getinvolved/portfolio.htm",
  "title": "portfolio - Grand Canyon National Park (U.S. National Park Service)",
  "html": "<body class=\"ParkSite\"><span aria-label=\"Top of page\" id=\"__topdoc__\" role=\"navigation\"></span>\n\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div id=\"beforeSkipLinks\" tabindex=\"-1\"></div>\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"GlobalHeader usaGlobalHeader\" role=\"banner\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-labelledby=\"exitModalLabel\" class=\"modal refreshableModal\" id=\"myModal\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h2 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"exitModalLabel\">Exiting nps.gov</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\"></div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Schedule\" id=\"cs_control_481716\"><div id=\"CS_Element_BannerContainer\" title=\"\"><div class=\"cs_GridRow\" id=\"gridRow_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_GridColumn\" id=\"gridCol_1_1_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_828672\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_7336411_828672\">\n\n</div></div><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_481828\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_7336411_481828\"> </div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div id=\"Park-header\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"pull-left\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div aria-label=\"Alerts Notification\" class=\"AlertsNotification\" data-site-code=\"grca\" id=\"AlertsNotification\" role=\"dialog\">\n<div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"AlertsNotification__Status visually-hidden\" role=\"status\">Loading alerts</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Panel\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Header\">\n<h2 class=\"Tag\" id=\"AlertsNotificationHeading\">Alerts In Effect</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Dismiss\" class=\"AlertsNotification__DismissButton\" type=\"button\">\nDismiss\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#close\"></use>\n</svg>\n</button>\n<span class=\"hr clearfix\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Body\" id=\"AlertsNotificationBody\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLinkContainer\">\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#add\"></use>\n</svg>\n<a class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLink\" href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/conditions.htm\" id=\"AlertsNotificationMoreLink\" tabindex=\"-1\">\nmore information on current conditions...\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"MainContent\" id=\"main\" role=\"main\">\n\n<div aria-labelledby=\"modal-contact-us-label\" class=\"modal fade\" id=\"modal-contact-us\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h4 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"modal-contact-us-label\">Contact Us</h4>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"adminTools\"></div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"ContentHeader text-content-size\">\n<h1 class=\"page-title\">Portfolio of Management Plans</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Layout\" id=\"cs_control_2\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"CS_Layout_Table\" id=\"cs_idLayout2\" summary=\"\" width=\"100%\"><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x1x1\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7336414\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<p>Park managers are guided by a variety of plans and studies, covering many topics. The totality of plans for a park is referred to as the Portfolio of Management Plans (portfolio). The portfolio is a dynamic compilation of planning guidance in which certain planning elements are removed and updated, or new elements are added as needed. Each<font color=\"#005999\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.25px;\"><b> </b></span></font>portfolio is composed of a unique set of plans designed specifically to help manage that NPS unit.<br/>\n<br/>\nBy using the totality of documents within a planning portfolio, park managers are enabled to fulfill all relevant legal and policy requirements, including general management plan statutory requirements. A park's planning portfolio, which extends from the foundation document to site-specific resource and visitor use management plans, creates a logical, trackable guide for future park management actions.</p>\n<p>Plans are prepared by interdisciplinary teams including the park superintendent and staff, landscape architects, community planners, specialists in natural and cultural resources, environmental design specialists, concessions management specialists, interpretation experts, and professionals in other fields, as needed. Public involvement is an essential element in the planning process and engaging with communities at an early stage in the process is important so that public input is considered as plans are developed, to inform agency decision-making.</p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7336433\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7336433\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2><b>Grand Canyon Portfolio</b></h2>\n<p> </p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7336859\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7336859\">\n<div class=\"Component FeatureGrid\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"FeatureGrid-item col-sm-6\">\n<div class=\"Component Feature -medium\">\n<a class=\"Feature-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/management/gmp.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send', 'event', 'Feature Grid - Prioritized', document.location.href, '/grca/learn/management/gmp.htm', 1, true)\">\n<div class=\"Feature-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"Several dozen sightseers watch the sunset at a scenic overlook at Grand Canyon National Park.\" class=\"Feature-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1380px) 640px, (min-width: 1200px) 550px, (min-width: 576px) 50vw, 100vw\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/38AFF255-A819-5C26-D80F9A2E31FF549E.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/38AFF255-A819-5C26-D80F9A2E31FF549E.jpg?width=420&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 420w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/38AFF255-A819-5C26-D80F9A2E31FF549E.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 640w\"/>\n<div class=\"Feature-title carrot-end\">General Management Plan</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"Feature-description\">The Grand Canyon National Park General Management Plan guides the management of resources, visitor use, and general development. </p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"FeatureGrid-item col-sm-6\">\n<div class=\"Component Feature -medium\">\n<a class=\"Feature-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/management/gmp.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send', 'event', 'Feature Grid - Prioritized', document.location.href, '/grca/learn/management/gmp.htm', 1, true)\">\n<div class=\"Feature-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"A conservator conducts mural conservation work in the Desert View Watchtower.\" class=\"Feature-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1380px) 640px, (min-width: 1200px) 550px, (min-width: 576px) 50vw, 100vw\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/61F087E6-B702-EC91-F4751C50E8424235.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/61F087E6-B702-EC91-F4751C50E8424235.jpg?width=420&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 420w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/61F087E6-B702-EC91-F4751C50E8424235.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 640w\"/>\n<div class=\"Feature-title carrot-end\">Foundation Document</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"Feature-description\">Explore the park's purpose, resources, history, and values. It's the foundation for planning and management. </p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"FeatureGrid-item col-sm-4\">\n<div class=\"Component Feature -small\">\n<a class=\"Feature-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/management/publications.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send', 'event', 'Feature Grid - Prioritized', document.location.href, '/grca/learn/management/publications.htm', 1, true)\">\n<div class=\"Feature-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"Construction workers position a large slab of stone for the Desert View amphitheater. \" class=\"Feature-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1380px) 420px, (min-width: 1200px) 360px, (min-width: 576px) 33vw, 100vw\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/FC36E658-BA9E-05F8-E1F7EB21361A3830.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/FC36E658-BA9E-05F8-E1F7EB21361A3830.jpg?width=420&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 420w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/FC36E658-BA9E-05F8-E1F7EB21361A3830.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 640w\"/>\n<div class=\"Feature-title carrot-end\">Strategic Plan</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"Feature-description\">Explore some of the major projects and emphasis areas planned across the park from 2020-2025. </p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"FeatureGrid-item col-sm-4\">\n<div class=\"Component Feature -small\">\n<a class=\"Feature-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/management/crmp.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send', 'event', 'Feature Grid - Prioritized', document.location.href, '/grca/learn/management/crmp.htm', 1, true)\">\n<div class=\"Feature-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"A commercial raft trip in oar boats on the Colorado River through Grand Canyon National Park.\" class=\"Feature-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1380px) 420px, (min-width: 1200px) 360px, (min-width: 576px) 33vw, 100vw\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/6239071E-ED0A-D557-E74F2673AE384107.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/6239071E-ED0A-D557-E74F2673AE384107.jpg?width=420&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 420w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/6239071E-ED0A-D557-E74F2673AE384107.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 640w\"/>\n<div class=\"Feature-title carrot-end\">Colorado River Management Plan</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"Feature-description\">Learn about the actions to conserve park resources while enhancing the visitor experience and river running recreational opportunities.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"FeatureGrid-item col-sm-4\">\n<div class=\"Component Feature -small\">\n<a class=\"Feature-link\" href=\"https://irma.nps.gov/DataStore/Reference/Profile/2266543\" onclick=\"gas('send', 'event', 'Feature Grid - Prioritized', document.location.href, 'https://irma.nps.gov/DataStore/Reference/Profile/2266543', 1, true)\">\n<div class=\"Feature-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"A view of Deer Creek during a rafting trip stop on the Colorado River.\" class=\"Feature-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1380px) 420px, (min-width: 1200px) 360px, (min-width: 576px) 33vw, 100vw\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/63EBA0A6-D986-1BA2-4D422401388407AF.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/63EBA0A6-D986-1BA2-4D422401388407AF.jpg?width=420&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 420w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/63EBA0A6-D986-1BA2-4D422401388407AF.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 640w\"/>\n<div class=\"Feature-title carrot-end\">Wilderness Character &amp; Monitoring</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"Feature-description\">Learn about Grand Canyon's wilderness character and efforts for its baseline monitoring assessment. </p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"FeatureGrid-item col-sm-4\">\n<div class=\"Component Feature -small\">\n<a class=\"Feature-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/management/trans.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send', 'event', 'Feature Grid - Prioritized', document.location.href, '/grca/learn/management/trans.htm', 1, true)\">\n<div class=\"Feature-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"A Tusayan Shuttle bus completes a stop in Tusayan on a return trip to Grand Canyon National Park.\" class=\"Feature-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1380px) 420px, (min-width: 1200px) 360px, (min-width: 576px) 33vw, 100vw\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/65E7F5FA-E1F7-D13D-37B18D82E24F362C.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/65E7F5FA-E1F7-D13D-37B18D82E24F362C.jpg?width=420&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 420w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/65E7F5FA-E1F7-D13D-37B18D82E24F362C.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 640w\"/>\n<div class=\"Feature-title carrot-end\">South Rim Transportation Plan</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"Feature-description\">Discover how the park is enhancing multimodal transportation options between Tusayan and the South Rim.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"FeatureGrid-item col-sm-4\">\n<div class=\"Component Feature -small\">\n<a class=\"Feature-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/management/overflights.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send', 'event', 'Feature Grid - Prioritized', document.location.href, '/grca/learn/management/overflights.htm', 1, true)\">\n<div class=\"Feature-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"A park helicopter waits near switchbacks on the South Kaibab Trail to assist an injured hiker. \" class=\"Feature-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1380px) 420px, (min-width: 1200px) 360px, (min-width: 576px) 33vw, 100vw\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/FA216C2A-D851-59EE-90A4C29009D010A5.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/FA216C2A-D851-59EE-90A4C29009D010A5.jpg?width=420&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 420w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/FA216C2A-D851-59EE-90A4C29009D010A5.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 640w\"/>\n<div class=\"Feature-title carrot-end\">Special Flight Rules Area</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"Feature-description\">Review the Draft EIS for management of overflight activity in Grand Canyon National Park to substantially restore natural quiet. </p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"FeatureGrid-item col-sm-4\">\n<div class=\"Component Feature -small\">\n<a class=\"Feature-link\" href=\"/grca/northrimstatus.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send', 'event', 'Feature Grid - Prioritized', document.location.href, '/grca/northrimstatus.htm', 1, true)\">\n<div class=\"Feature-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"Visitors sit at the Grand Canyon Lodge veranda to watch the sunset from the North Rim.\" class=\"Feature-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1380px) 420px, (min-width: 1200px) 360px, (min-width: 576px) 33vw, 100vw\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/65976F53-9D5D-BE98-D2CAE417645364A2.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/65976F53-9D5D-BE98-D2CAE417645364A2.jpg?width=420&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 420w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/65976F53-9D5D-BE98-D2CAE417645364A2.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 640w\"/>\n<div class=\"Feature-title carrot-end\">North Rim Status</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"Feature-description\">Learn about the current status of the North Rim.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7337073\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7347089\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7347089\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2>Additional and Archived Plans<a name=\"onthisPage-1\"></a></h2>\n<p>Additional plans and environmental documents for the National Park Service are available on the <strong><a href=\"https://parkplanning.nps.gov/\" id=\"https://parkplanning.nps.gov/|\">Planning, Environment and Public Comment site</a></strong> (PEPC). PEPC is an online collaborative tool dedicated to facilitating the National Environmental Policy Act/National Historic Preservation Act process in conservation planning, environmental impact analysis, and informed decision-making.<br/>\n<br/>\nOther options include contacting the Grand Canyon Museum Collection or checking the NPS <a href=\"https://pubs.nps.gov/\" id=\"anch_21\">Electronic Technical Information Center</a>.</p>\n</div></div>\n</td></tr>\n</table></div>\n</div><!-- col-sm-12 -->\n</div><!-- row -->\n</div><!-- ColumnMain col-sm-9 -->\n</div><!-- ColumnGrid row -->\n</div><!-- end container -->\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 text-content-size text-content-style\">\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\">Last updated: February 24, 2026</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n <!-- ParkFooter -->\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div><!-- end of <div main> -->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!-- the rest of the scripts are leftovers from before the centennial down and should be pared down where possible -->\n\n<link href=\"/common/commonspot/templates/assets/libs/colorbox/colorbox.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n\n<div class=\"modal fade\" id=\"outdated-browser\" role=\"dialog\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n</div>\n</body>",
  "scraped_at": "2026-04-06T13:54:24Z"
